title: When League meets Fire Emblem

embed.description: You expected me to do the "Rumble in the jungle"-joke, didn't you? Well okay, here it is: there is Rumble in the jungle. Now gtfo.

body:
Hey guys,

I made a montage and tried to bring in some very special effects. :P Would love some feedback on it!

See ya

replies.body:
Shit. Another human who knows what Fire Emblem is. Its a miracle.

Shame the scene was dodge, more so when you have random Japanese which doesn't match. 

But at least you know what Fire Emblem is.
